scaledlibsizes.Rd

Get tmm-scaled libsizes

scaledlibsizes(counts)

Arguments

counts

counts matri

Value

scaled libsize vector

Examples

file <- download_data('billing19.rnacounts.txt')
object <- read_rnaseq_counts(file, cpm=FALSE, log2=FALSE, plot=FALSE)
